{"word":"G1601 - ἐκπίπτω - ekpíptō - ek-pip'-to - Be cast","slug":"G1601","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ekpíptō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ek-pip'-to"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be cast"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9; - ekpipto&#x0304;</b> - <i>ek-pip'-to</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>drop away</i>; specifically <i>be driven out</i> of one&rsquo;s course; figuratively to <i>lose</i>, <i>become inefficient:</i> - be cast, fail, fall (away, off), take none effect."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431\">G4431</a>"}]}